Although you define `in1`, `in2`, and `out` as 32-bit ports in your module (as indicated by your comment), the connected signals in your testbench are only 1 bit wide. Therefore, only the first bit of your module&#39;s input signals (i.e., `in1[0]` and `in2[0]`) are driven.

Try to use the following testbench:

